    "text": "Long Island Sound Restoration and Stewardship Reauthorization Act of 2025\n\nThis bill reauthorizes the Environmental Protection Agency's Long Island Sound programs through FY2029. The programs, which include\u00a0a stewardship grant program, focus on conserving and restoring the estuary off the coast of New York and Connecticut."
